-- Nikkei 225 May Options Settle at 9,019.35, Traders Say
-- B y   Y o s h i a k i   N o h a r a
-- 2012-05-11T00:18:54Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-11/nikkei-225-may-options-settle-at-9-019-35-traders-say.html
Japan ’s Nikkei 225 May options
settled at 9,019.35, traders said.  The Nikkei 225 Stock Average rose 0.2 percent to 9,030.57
as of 9:14 a.m. in Tokyo. The gauge closed at 9,009.65 yesterday.
The settlement price, also known as the “special quotation,”
of Nikkei 225 options is calculated after all stocks on the
benchmark equity gauge begin trading.  To contact the reporter for this story:
Yoshiaki Nohara in Tokyo at 
